#
# Info about the MTBMap style
#

summary: MTBMap style

version=1.0

description {
MTBMap style with the following colouring of MTB trails:
1. Green - mtb:scale == 0
2. Blue  - mtb:scale == 1
3. Red   - mtb:scale == 2
4. Black - mtb:scale == 3

-- Do not draw unhuman scales 4-6

* Yellow highlight for recommended trails (class:bicycle:mtb == 1 or class:bicycle:mtb == 2)
* Orange/Pink highlight for top recommended trails (class:bicycle:mtb == 3)
* Pale green/blue/red/black colour for non-recommended trails (class:bicycle:mtb < 0)
}
